name: Higher Power
description: Higher Power is a cross between the hybrid strain Geezus and the sativa African Queen bred by Wild Oregon Weed.  It has a delicious odor akin to grape Froot Loops and has been measured at 24% THC.  This sativa offers a truly stimulating high that will leave you energized and bursting with creativity.
